column11:
  We report our detailed calculation of the infrared spectra of GaAs and GaP
from first principles, and similar ongoing efforts for diamond-type spectra,
which have recently been calculated.

column5:
3 pages; Presented at Meson 2004: 8th International Workshop on Meson
  Production, Properties and Interaction, Krakow, Poland, 4-8 June 2004;
  Submitted to International Journal of Modern Physics A
